{"tid":1874960,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【超市慌乜撚都缺貨】 魷魚絲都無慘形同坐監","createTime":"2020-02-11T13:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T01:08:21.000Z","uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"91bfd4e8e98b34d90ec50e73ca8a61b93dc043b8","tid":1874960,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5mA7xqi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5mA7xqi.jpg&h=5461284b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傍晚去咗屋企附近間惠康諗住買包金龜嘜魷魚絲咬下，鬧饑荒咁款一包都無上架，諗起以前去荔枝角買四大俾裏面坐嘅朋友&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家香港人有個咁嘅濕鳩政府，真係衰撚過坐監！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978bad26fc8079c72ce91d66b281eb644786dc4c","tid":1874960,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f65e45c0dbe906f3013833091d6b88daf8d14b","tid":1874960,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"去水晶屋啦"},{"pid":"8951b5a97fa930f874693d3b22e7248d592067e6","tid":1874960,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27f65e45c0dbe906f3013833091d6b88daf8d14b","tid":1874960,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"去水晶屋啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T18:28:26.000Z","msg":"多謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我大鄉里第一次聽呢間嘢，或者其實係以前幫襯過但唔知個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://m.facebook.com/crystalhouse7046/&amp;ved=2ahUKEwit2IT_jsrnAhXCxYsBHRyDBPQQjjgwAHoECAEQAQ&amp;usg=AOvVaw25rLyyfkCeE44i_bdqiLLW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fur